Honor Logo Honor is a smartphone brand owned by Shenzhen Zhixin New Information Technology Co., Ltd. It was formerly owned by Huawei Technologies. As part of the former owner Huawei Consumer Business Group’s dual-brand strategy, Honor provides smartphone handsets targeting young consumers but has released tablet computers and wearable technology as well.
